content: On February 11, a fire broke out outside the Spring Expo Park in Heze, Shandong Province, and a number of cars parked at the entrance were burned. Video footage showed a fierce fire, thick smoke, and occasional crackling explosions. Witnesses said the incident occurred around 4 p.m., and a total of six cars were burned and scrapped, leaving only empty shells.
